次献血浆，并非网传的多次献血，且献血浆最短间隔为 14 天，其活动时长也合理。」上述工作人员还表示，这家血站拥有合法资质，要通过持身份证件及人脸识别的方式以及最低时限要求才能献血浆。对于网友质疑献血浆成助学一事，工作人员表示将和血站联系沟通。 公开信息显示，献血浆是借助专业的血浆机或血液分离机，将捐献者血液中的血浆和血细胞分离出来，只保留血浆，而血细胞还会输回到捐赠者身体中。献血通常需要 3-4 个月的时间才可以恢复，献血浆的恢复时间短得多，一般 2 周左右即可恢复正常。山西一血站献血浆助学活动引争议 当地卫健局：合法合规 将进行沟通 _ 和顺县 _ 补助 _ 才能"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-87b1ea3c723ca4ceb5795e0f36e99630_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665415916"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIgJT3tdrjsKEPEAMaCTExMDE0Nzc1OSDhibW2BjAAOMsGQBpyCTY2NTQxNTkxNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1725199415.739562", "card_id": "Q_619426866", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 116}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价马龙这个运动员?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如何评价马龙这个运动员"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-9d42e0a1e9f15e1125e264a45db11ae2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/619426866"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IgJT3tdrjsKEPEAMaCDk5OTMwNTY4IOvMracGMAA4oAJAG3IJNjE5NDI2ODY2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1725199415.739901", "card_id": "Q_665595533", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 144}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《边水往事》大结局？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-14b18cdb736712bef3f663b90b46d7be_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "热度累计中", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/665595533"